title: Звёздная кухня
overview: TV presenter Olga Buzova and restaurateur Alexey Vasilchuk invite guests to the star restaurant, where artists, comedians and bloggers will meet in a culinary battle. They will have to prepare famous dishes from all cuisines of the world on their own, and the winner will be determined by experts of the restaurant business. To make cooking more interesting, the stars will face challenging and fun culinary challenges.
